readable.content: A couple in a red canoe paddle down a rough river lined with trees . Two paddlers in a red canoe approach a couple of large rocks in the rushing river with conifers in the background . Two people are in a canoe . Two people canoeing down a river in a red canoe . Two people paddle a canoe down a rough stretch of river near a pine forest .
